{"id":144453,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：华为与摩托罗拉达庭外和解/","date":"2011-04-13T20:30:22Z","modified":"2011-04-13T20:30:22Z","title":"简讯：华为与摩托罗拉达庭外和解","content":"<div>\n<p>华为与摩托罗拉就一宗涉及商业秘密纠纷达成和解，为摩托罗拉向诺基亚西门子出售一业务部门铺平道路。</p>\n<p>华为指摩托罗拉向诺西出售网络业务将导致华为的诸多商业秘密泄露给竞争对手。</p>\n<p>摩托罗拉是华为的长期合作伙伴。</p>\n<p>根据和解协议，摩托罗拉同意支付华为一笔数目不详的技术转让费。</p>\n<p>摩托罗拉网络业务的出让价格从12亿美元降到9.75亿美元，以便交易在4月底之前完成。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/business/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QG5RmbdcYey2Urk9x7GVNdljPG4/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QG5RmbdcYey2Urk9x7GVNdljPG4/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QG5RmbdcYey2Urk9x7GVNdljPG4/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QG5RmbdcYey2Urk9x7GVNdljPG4/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/1nUSnMqKucY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？请电邮订阅数字时代 <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}